# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.4.0] - 2023-06-22

### Added

- [storybook] Make stories editable
- [footer] Large footer as an option (default true)
- [docs] Add react-toastfy as a technology
- [sidemenu] Add top property

### Changed

- [packages] Upgrade dependencies

### Fixed

- [sidemenu] Group button closing on click

## [0.3.0] - 2023-05-30

### Added

- [PageWithAuth] New component to avoid boilerplate code on required auth pages
- [docs] Usage guide for new components

### Fixed

- [storybook] Broken link

## [0.2.1] - 2023-05-29

### Fixed

- [dialog] Children max width
- [storybook] Logo size
- Code smells
- Code duplications

## [0.2.0] - 2023-05-26

### Added

- [Page] New property to override default toastContainer

### Changed

- [toast] Toast interface exported directly from react-toastfy

## [0.1.6] - 2023-05-23

### Fixed

- [dialog] Default visibility false
- [footer] Default footer links order

## [0.1.5] - 2023-05-19

### Fixed

- [Storybook] Button to popup dialogs
- [Storybook] Translate to english

### Added

- [footer] Signature text
- [Storybook] Homepage and docs

## [0.1.4] - 2023-05-08

### Fixed

- Empty SideMenu
- Issue template

